Sahaja Yogi: Guilty. Shri Mata Ji:
You see first he asked me the question,

00:33:37.421 --> 00:33:43.803
" Why there is dippresion
without being guilty?"

00:33:43.853 --> 00:33:47.808
If one get possessed,
you feel to get possessed,

00:33:47.832 --> 00:33:51.787
but somehow you never
reach poise.

00:33:51.827 --> 00:33:54.169
who talk of separation.

00:33:54.194 --> 00:34:00.127
You need some quarenstile,

00:34:00.144 --> 00:34:07.500
you allow brothers to
attend in Sahaj Yoga.

00:34:07.525 --> 00:34:10.484
Don’t you listen to
Sahaja Yoga with great

00:34:10.508 --> 00:34:13.975
interest? [Unclear] Then
whom do you listen to?

