[Unclear]

00:36:04.008 --> 00:36:07.513
This will definitely lead to
depression if you mix up with

00:36:07.537 --> 00:36:11.351
such people. If you dwell with
such people, you won’t ascend.

00:36:11.376 --> 00:36:17.250
Having attained it, by
staying with such people—

00:36:17.275 --> 00:36:19.001
—joy.

00:36:19.026 --> 00:36:24.580
Understood, right?

